<plot>Wife of a B-lister, mommy of two... Nikki Wall is a housewife in Orange County, California, who also happens to be the manager of a very low budget filmmaker who goes by the name of 'Creep Creepersin' - who also happens to be her husband. Nikki contends with homemade film horrors like Vaginal Holocaust and The Brothers Cannibal while baking her own bread, doing the laundry, homeschooling her two kids, and nurturing the 'vision' of her husband with an admitted level of submission. Without a day job, Creep must keep the movies flowing so they make enough money to survive - but when does Nikki get to do her own thing, and when does she get to take a break to do it?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?082887</url></doc>
